item.title: RAATD Database
item.author: nicolas.casajus@fondationbiodiversite.fr (FRB-CESAB)
item.description: Tracking data for multiple species of Antarctic meso- and top-predators to identify Areas of Ecological Significance. This dataset is a compilation of data from 12 national Antarctic programs, and including data from 17 predator species, 4,060 individual animals, and over 2.9 million locations.
